main event: A UFO was observed over Riceville, Iowa on August 20, 1955.
interesting points: The observation lasted for 3 minutes,The object was assessed as likely being a balloon,The report mentioned the possibility of the light being Arcturus,There was no photograph present in the document,The comparison to Arcturus indicated an astronomical explanation for the sighting.
sighted object: one unidentified object in the sky
witness description: A ground visual observation by an unidentified witness.
